SUMMARY:Flyering Day
CLASS:PUBLIC
DESCRIPTION:Feb 15th 2026 Flyering Day at 10am. *Location Deep South Philly
  - West of Broad*\n\n\n\n\n**What to Expect**\nOn Flyering Day we put up f
 lyers for our upcoming events and outreach initiatives\nWe like the buddy 
 system! Pairs walk together putting up flyers while they chat and hang out
 .\nWe’ll be using tools like staple guns and wheat paste\n\n**Why Join F
 lyering Day?**\nlow lift! It’s easy work.\nfun! You get to know your com
 rades as you walk around together\nfulfilling! You’ll be supporting outr
 each ✨IRL✨ (aka not on social media)
CATEGORIES:General Membership Events
DTSTAMP:20260412T120032Z
CREATED:20260204T175751Z
END:VEVENT
