URL:https://cryptpad.fr/doc/#/2/doc/view/aEB-ij7WqdBHe27D8XSvRRxJbnR7e4jyvQ
 nPBf4ZrOo/
LOCATION:Philadelphia Ethical Societ 1906 South Rittenhouse Square
SUMMARY:Winter General Assembly
CLASS:PUBLIC
DESCRIPTION:Our General Assembly is officially booked for Sunday\, February
  22nd at 4:30PM at Ethical Society in Center City. Mark your calendars!\n\
 nWe also open our call for proposals. Any member in good standing can subm
 it a proposal\, which can be a project proposal requesting a budget allotm
 ent or a policy proposal. Consult our guide to writing proposals here (htt
 ps://cryptpad.fr/doc/#/2/doc/view/aEB-ij7WqdBHe27D8XSvRRxJbnR7e4jyvQnPBf4Z
 rOo/). \n\nAny member can also run for any of the available Central Commit
 tee positions in the  Constitution (https://static1.squarespace.com/static
 /59cb1893edaed8670cb27244/t/59f7a88d6c319421a027d291/1509402765969/Constit
 ution+--+2017+appoved.pdf). Right now\,  the Secretary and 2 out of the 5 
 arbiter positions are open. \n\nPost your proposal or intention to run in 
 the ⁠general-assemblies channel. The deadline to submit a proposal or an
 nounce your intention to run for a position is 48 hours before the GA\, so
  4:30PM on Friday\, February 20th.\n\nThe agenda will be posted closer to 
 the event.
CATEGORIES:General Membership Events
DTSTAMP:20260412T120032Z
CREATED:20260131T183128Z
END:VEVENT
