BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:KDIG2382768312
DTSTART:20260307T170000Z
SEQUENCE:0
TRANSP:OPAQUE
DTEND:20260307T203000Z
LOCATION:Kingsessing Library (1201 S 51st St)
SUMMARY:TUF Clothing Swap
CLASS:PUBLIC
DESCRIPTION:Join us on Saturday\, March 7th from 12-3:30pm for a clothing s
 wap organized by Trans United Front (TUF) at the Kingsessing Library (1201
  S 51st St). We will be accepting clothing until 1:30pm\; after that\, jus
 t browsing and swapping!\n\nTUF is a project in Philly Socialists that see
 ks to facilitate connection\, mutual aid\, and solidarity between intercon
 nected political struggles within the Philadelphia trans community.\n\nYou
 're welcome to bring up to two bags of clean clothes you no longer wear (p
 erhaps because they are no longer gender affirming) and swap with others w
 ho might have clothing that feels more affirming and comfortable! \n\nWe h
 ope a lot of trans folks attend\, but all are welcome\, especially familie
 s and community members in need of clothing. We will have child-sized clot
 hing at this swap for the first time(!!)\n\nMasks encouraged and provided!
  Event space is wheelchair accessible. Please reach out via DMs with any f
 urther accessibility questions.\n\nSolidarity forever! See you there!
CATEGORIES:T.U.F. - Trans United Front
DTSTAMP:20260412T120032Z
CREATED:20260301T124420Z
END:VEVENT
